    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per the agreed project scope, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission. Note: the experimental baseline dataset and geometry scan dataset carry vintages from Q3–Q4 2025, predating the v3 model revision finalized in February 2026. Re-validation of these datasets against the updated model geometry is planned for the next assessment cycle.",
